00:28:33,070 --> 00:28:35,474
to account for the smaller
luminal diameter.

578
00:28:35,499 --> 00:28:37,481
The cavalry has arrived,

579
00:28:37,575 --> 00:28:39,644
though I can already sense
there are way too many

