764
00:40:00,833 --> 00:40:02,253
Okay, so I don't get it.

765
00:40:02,277 --> 00:40:05,092
Why didn't you tell him
how you felt about him?

766
00:40:05,188 --> 00:40:06,648
- Maybe I did.
- No.

767
00:40:06,672 --> 00:40:08,947
